    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是潜入系统的病毒，要摧毁它。击退成群的杀毒软件。 不断进化，适应环境，与所有阻碍你的人战斗。摧毁系统的一个又一个部分，造成尽可能多的破坏。即使你的病毒被摧毁，也会有其他病毒取而代之！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297120/extras/cae52dba4e37b559a72e4b291d163409.poster.avif?t=1732318600\" width=474 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297120/extras/cae52dba4e37b559a72e4b291d163409.webm?t=1732318600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297120/extras/cae52dba4e37b559a72e4b291d163409.mp4?t=1732318600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >入侵与摧毁》是一款复古风格的roguelite-FPS游戏。你需要射击敌人并摧毁关卡中的所有物体。前者可以获得经验，用于升级和购买新武器。其次是宝贵的资源，可用于改进下一次入侵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试试这款受早期游戏机和 FPS 游戏氛围启发的沉思游戏吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择适合你的图像模式--复古或纯净画面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297120/extras/8307525e0211a80d4f17858963526e5d.poster.avif?t=1732318600\" width=474 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297120/extras/8307525e0211a80d4f17858963526e5d.webm?t=1732318600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297120/extras/8307525e0211a80d4f17858963526e5d.mp4?t=1732318600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
